Program: Discovery
Title: This year's most essential science books
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrwl3
Last Broadcast Date: 18 December 1995
Experts help compile a list of science reading from texts published throughout 1995. Science editor of the Daily Telegraph Roger Highfield and astronomer Paul Murdin help presenter Roland Pease to compile a list of science reading from texts published throughout 1995.